 ones.\nI have 2 groups of plants. One with label \"Sansevieria dooneri\" (a synonym of S. parva) and one with label \"Sansevieria senegambica\" and sadly both groups look awfully the same at first sight.<\/p>\n","question_id":20722,"tags":["botany","species-identification","species","identification"],"score":2,"accepted_answer_id":20726,"down_vote_count":0,"is_answered":true,"view_count":56,"up_vote_count":2},{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/54a82fba3ce9f146c47e561b973f6adf?s=128&d=identicon&r=PG&f=1","user_type":"registered","user_id":5851,"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/users/5851/caters","reputation":341,"display_name":"Caters","accept_rate":36},"answers":[{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/7bace80d8320bb4c10619035e675b838?s=128&d=identicon&r=PG","user_type":"registered","user_id":8809,"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/users/8809/nick-sandor","reputation":720,"display_name":"Nick Sandor"},"score":4,"is_accepted":false,"comments":[{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/14a225b416674b1d9fb6cf14554d5054?s=128&d=identicon&r=PG","user_type":"registered","user_id":8709,"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/users/8709/boncodigo","reputation":289,"display_name":"bonCodigo","accept_rate":100},"score":1,"post_id":20712,"edited":false,"creation_date":1408765880,"comment_id":32315,"body":"did you mean &quot;breathing rate&quot; in <code>it&#39;s not like heart rate or bleeding rate are regulated by pulmonary arteries<\/code>?"},{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/7bace80d8320bb4c10619035e675b838?s=128&d=identicon&r=PG","user_type":"registered","user_id":8809,"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/users/8809/nick-sandor","reputation":720,"display_name":"Nick Sandor"},"score":0,"post_id":20712,"reply_to_user":{"profile_image":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/14a225b416674b1d9fb6cf14554d5054?s=128&d=identicon&r=PG","user_type":"registered","user_id":8709,"link":"ht