an embryos is \"make it female\". <\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n\n<p><strong>Q<\/strong>: How did Alfred Jost actually perform this experiment?<\/p>\n\n<p>Essentially I'm after a less superficial description of how Jost implemented this experiment in practice.<\/p>\n\n<p>I did a bit of Googling; what I found was consistent with Hank's description, but still omits a description of <em>how<\/em> Jost excised rabbit embryo gonads (instead just asserting that he did it).<\/p>\n","question_id":20683,"tags":["reproduction","experiment"],"score":6,"accepted_answer_id":20713,"down_vote_count":0,"is_answered":true,"view_count":841,"up_vote_count":6},{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://i.stack.imgur.com/DFxSs.png?s=128&g=1","user_type":"registered","user_id":8891,"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/users/8891/simontemplar","reputation":113,"display_name":"simontemplar"},"comments":[{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/7bace80d8320bb4c10619035e675b838?s=128&d=identicon&r=PG","user_type":"registered","user_id":8809,"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/users/8809/nick-sandor","reputation":720,"display_name":"Nick Sandor"},"score":1,"post_id":20706,"edited":false,"creation_date":1408724071,"comment_id":32279,"body":"To answer your first question, just search &quot;plague&quot; in Google News: &quot;Just last month the Chinese government sealed off a city of more than 100,000 people, fearing the spread of a plague outbreak.&quot;, and even &quot;Struggling Liberia creates &#39;plague villages&#39; in Ebola epicentre&quot;. The way poor people deal with plague changed from the times they thought the miasma is to blame, to the point that it is a model for fighting other epidemics. Also, the antibiotics are only 70 years old: old enough to be patent free and easily manufactured. China and India are in fact top manufacturers for such drugs."},{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/1b3c5b025ca581db5a8fdd2564b5367c?s=128&d=identicon&r=PG&f=1","