dy materials.<\/p>\n\n<p>Aorta can<\/p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>it keeps blood flowing<\/li>\n<li>it can accumulate potential energy for bumping and compression <\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n<p><strong>However, why aorta is called chamber and particularly compression chamber?<\/strong>\nI heard this term today first time.<\/p>\n","question_id":14900,"tags":["physiology","cardiology"],"score":0,"accepted_answer_id":20598,"down_vote_count":0,"is_answered":true,"view_count":87,"up_vote_count":0,"last_edit_date":1391802509},{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/145b25ae167dbe8a844ab9e9531ac0e6?s=128&d=identicon&r=PG&f=1","user_type":"registered","user_id":8794,"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/users/8794/oli","reputation":31,"display_name":"Oli"},"comments":[{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/da1e8af33e12bfa60ea44b3af00c0d03?s=128&d=identicon&r=PG&f=1","user_type":"moderator","user_id":5144,"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/users/5144/chris","reputation":31001,"display_name":"Chris"},"score":0,"post_id":20554,"edited":false,"creation_date":1408226779,"comment_id":31954,"body":"So you have the problem that your blank is too high?"},{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/145b25ae167dbe8a844ab9e9531ac0e6?s=128&d=identicon&r=PG&f=1","user_type":"registered","user_id":8794,"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/users/8794/oli","reputation":31,"display_name":"Oli"},"score":0,"post_id":20554,"edited":false,"creation_date":1408227071,"comment_id":31957,"body":"Yeah, the enzyme blank is high"},{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/da1e8af33e12bfa60ea44b3af00c0d03?s=128&d=identicon&r=PG&f=1","user_type":"moderator","user_id":5144,"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/users/5144/chris","reputation":31001,"display_name":"Chris"},"score":0,"post_id":20554,"edited":false,"creation_date":1408227103,"comment_id":31958,"body":"Can you exclude having a contamination?"},{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://www